---
import ArticleLayout from '../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';
---

<ArticleLayout
  title="Aerodynamics Consultancy | Wavey Dynamics"
  heading="AERODYNAMICS CONSULTANCY"
  subheading="Reach your ambitions."
  image="/images/pages/community-hero.jpg"
  imagePosition="center"
  description="CFD simulation, wind tunnel support and aerodynamic component development for motorsport and high-performance automotive applications from Wavey Dynamics."
>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Working extensively with vehicle dynamics in any performance application, the art of aerodynamics can enhance or detract from a platform's competitiveness. This relationship motivates us towards excellence in both specialities. Whether you're maximising downforce or optimising your EV efficiency, we're equipped get you there.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">In projects involving fluid dynamics today, Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD) is an essential companion to develop and understand a particular flow case. Combining this with a thorough understanding of fluid flow fundamentals, provides the benefit of lowering costs, reduced development times and the ability to find multiple design iterations &amp; concepts without physically building the model.</p>

  <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">Combining our knowledge with the latest tools and techniques and a holistic approach, we are enabled to help you with automotive and motorsport applications including:</p>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Development</h2>
  <ul class="wd-list mb-10 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>3D scanning and model development
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>CAD generation</li>
        <li>Reverse engineering</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Whole vehicle Aero Platform Development
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Overall lift/drag efficiency</li>
        <li>Drag reduction</li>
        <li>Scaling performance</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Wing Tunnel Support
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Scale model testing</li>
        <li>Aerodynamic Mapping</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Aerodynamic Component Development
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Wings</li>
        <li>Splitters</li>
        <li>Diffusers</li>
        <li>Undertray development</li>
        <li>Drag devices and other flow control devices</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Aerodynamic Modelling
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Including surfacing</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Flow Visualisation</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Simulation</h2>
  <ul class="wd-list mb-10 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD)
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Lift &amp; drag optimisation</li>
        <li>Aerodynamic efficiency optimisation</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">Always striving for new experience, we also value opportunities to transfer our knowledge to benefit other industries.</p>

  <a href="/contact" class="inline-block border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors">Get in Touch →</a>

</ArticleLayout>
